    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的 Chinoy：印度储备银行需要介入以促进经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/jpmorgan-s-chinoy-rbi-needs-to-step-in-to-boost-growth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通董事总经理兼首席印度经济学家 Sajjid Chinoy 在接受彭博电视采访时表示，由于政府仍处于财政整顿模式，印度央行将不得不承担大量促进经济增长的重任。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/jpmorgan-s-chinoy-rbi-needs-to-step-in-to-boost-growth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华宝和伯克希尔哈撒韦同意以 30 亿美元收购 Triumph</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/warburg-berkshire-partners-agree-to-3-billion-deal-for-triumph</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权公司华平投资和伯克希尔合伙公司同意以约 30 亿美元（包括债务）的价格将飞机零部件和服务供应商 Triumph Group Inc. 私有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/warburg-berkshire-partners-agree-to-3-billion-deal-for-triumph</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊圣托里尼旅游中心进入地震高度警戒状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-tourist-hub-of-santorini-on-high-earthquake-alert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两天，希腊圣托里尼岛发生多起小地震，当地政府发布紧急状态，警惕这一热门旅游胜地发生大地震。目前，该岛的学校已关闭，也不鼓励公众集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-tourist-hub-of-santorini-on-high-earthquake-alert</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟检察官在印度钢铁欺诈案中瞄准德国公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/eu-prosecutors-target-german-company-in-indian-steel-fraud-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲检察官突击搜查了一家德国公司的办公室，该公司涉嫌实施涉及印度钢铁进口的欺诈计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/eu-prosecutors-target-german-company-in-indian-steel-fraud-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:02:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀意外加速，支持欧洲央行谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/euro-zone-inflation-unexpectedly-quickens-backing-ecb-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区通胀意外加速，支持欧洲央行谨慎降低利率，而疲软的经济则面临来自美国日益加剧的贸易威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/euro-zone-inflation-unexpectedly-quickens-backing-ecb-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾宣布进入粮食安全紧急状态以控制大米价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/philippines-declares-food-security-emergency-to-tame-rice-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周一宣布进入粮食安全紧急状态，以降低大米价格。官员称，尽管大幅削减关税，大米价格仍然居高不下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/philippines-declares-food-security-emergency-to-tame-rice-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 09:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税措施后投资者纷纷涌向美元避险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/wall-street-backs-the-dollar-s-wild-rally-to-gather-steam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团和摩根大通等华尔街银行认为，即使在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税举措导致美元飙升之后，购买美元仍然可以赚到很多钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/wall-street-backs-the-dollar-s-wild-rally-to-gather-steam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>滞胀风险导致美国国债收益率曲线自 11 月以来最趋平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国总统唐纳德·特朗普向主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举动将加剧通胀并损害经济增长，美国短期债券暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发通胀和经济增长担忧，金属价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，贸易战可能加剧全球经济增长，从铜到铁矿石等工业金属价格随之暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：关税导致美元上涨、股指期货下跌 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国开始征收关税并引发威胁全球经济增长的贸易战，美元飙升，股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
